{"tid":174362,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"撞車claim保險一問","createTime":"2017-03-26T17:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T15:25:48.000Z","uid":4583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcca71ed4631e7ce7326bac877b0248086364815","tid":174362,"uid":4583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"小弟尋日腳殘，前車突然急煞，收唔切撞左佢<br />\n都知自己衰<br />\n不過目測對方架車傷得唔嚴重，係佢尾bumper鬆左<br />\n報左警，同對方交換左contact<br />\n同對方傾和解，佢話等車房睇左先<br />\n咁今日報返黎話要整萬三蚊，話要訂新件<br />\n傾下收少啲佢都唔肯讓步，咁唯有報保險<br />\n想問下因爲撞正紅日，報唔到保險，星期一報會否太遲？<br />\n另外之後係咪要請一日假去交通部，同一日上court(假設我俾人告不小心駕駛) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因份工要預早攞假<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c45ba0327d0874583a55b63d3ed1f74e926088f","tid":174362,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:12:31.000Z","msg":"Lm 學野"},{"pid":"ce2002fac5447ddf77ffdd9ce8312d8ecf148ff4","tid":174362,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:13:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"547f15b87cedeebda9f309e43934d2f27d776f35","tid":174362,"uid":10295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:20:27.000Z","msg":"一萬幾千比啦"},{"pid":"71231fc91ac8678455fa7d23efe3625a6c25a38d","tid":174362,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"萬三比人啦"},{"pid":"26065d622a4eda2eb7d4be7dae30392ff5a0ad05","tid":174362,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T20:53:35.000Z","msg":"13k比啦<br />\n自己錯晒冇得講<br />\n有限錢姐<br />\n又上庭又扣分又剩為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201a3a0a2b0bdc967a241e361d40a5f883d5f7df","tid":174362,"uid":4583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>13k比啦<br />\n自己錯晒冇得講<br />\n有限錢姐<br />\n又上庭又扣分又剩為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk